{"tid":531217,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"連13歲既GEM唱月半小夜曲都有感情過唱左30年既李克勤，可笑嗎？","createTime":"2018-01-16T14:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T18:33:35.000Z","uid":49388,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"328ee9df2d788e3cc6965a98444b4ab4752b1c2b","tid":531217,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"首月半小夜曲唱足三十年都唔及自己後輩翻唱好聽同有感情。李克勤你好去死吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吧<br />\n<br />\n1.陳樂基<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RmbwIh5Kf6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRmbwIh5Kf6g&d=DwHQS8vmyL0yqodkq4Oyuxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=5304d7bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RmbwIh5Kf6g</a><br />\n有D人話月半唔應該咁唱，但我想講，無可否認陳樂基演譯所投入既感情係比李克勤多，亦比李克勤更易觸動人，而我認為音樂既原意就係表達情感，唱歌感情理應放係頭位，加上陳樂基係副歌既爆發力係李克勤做唔到，所以係呢首歌上陳樂基係比李克勤優勝。<br />\n<br />\n2.容袓兒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qyeiBZv6tQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqyeiBZv6tQc&d=DwHQS8vmyL0yqodkq4Oyuxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=52532662\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qyeiBZv6tQc</a><br />\nJoey版本風格上對比陳樂基係比較貼近原版，加上編曲風格dark味較重，淒怨味多左唔少。唔理感情，月半呢首歌原版係比rock版較為適合，而joey版本跟番原版風格，加上joey漸漸由淺入深既深情演譯，係李克勤永遠都做唔到，亦係女版中最成功既翻唱。<br />\n<br />\n3.GEM<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PKEmgy6_qlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPKEmgy6_qlE&d=DwHQS8vmyL0yqodkq4Oyuxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=fb34f44c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PKEmgy6_qlE</a><br />\n當時得13歲既蝗漿已經唱到咁，有少少感染力已經將李克勤比下去，係阿漿勁定李克勤太廢？<br />\n<br />\n4.李克勤<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lkR_mmqp1Pk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlkR_mmqp1Pk&d=DwHQS8vmyL0yqodkq4Oyuxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=9c95fc31\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lkR_mmqp1Pk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kanpP_zg-54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkanpP_zg-54&d=DwHQS8vmyL0yqodkq4Oyuxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=f2dd114f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kanpP_zg-54</a><br />\n李克勤就唔洗講，30年唱腔一成不變，感情相對繼續較弱，好既就話佢keep得好，衰既就話佢悶。依家把聲更開始退化易沙，過多幾年到把聲死埋，又無感情，好快連剩餘價值都消失，到時真係變死剩種。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8VDCaldp4qc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8VDCaldp4qc&d=DwHQS8vmyL0yqodkq4Oyuxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=7a9b4f09\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8VDCaldp4qc</a><br />\n但講到尾，都係原唱太勁，無人夠佢好聽，包括容祖兒。<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n河合奈保子&gt;容祖兒&gt;GEM&gt;陳樂基&gt;李克勤"},{"pid":"3b737a199ef784594576936439ea09f5c0955b90","tid":531217,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f486df7871fc1fc5f3b92da92b8285ac114ef23","tid":531217,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0adef4e16f66277e83bfd855ff2d38d103bc7f3","tid":531217,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f486df7871fc1fc5f3b92da92b8285ac114ef23","tid":531217,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"有佢墊底李克勤唔使死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a41f6470d9d49697b6ef53f953b39f1cd79c6ef","tid":531217,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"唱腔老套無感情發聲機械一成不變恃老賣老但極之好客既香港樂壇廢柴人端送禮勤李克勤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c913982dc3ae24f945dca9c2a6c0a928d10abbc","tid":531217,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"以前啲日本人唱得真係好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7135a0213e6d9f31e92f51f2038b71a9d2866a","tid":531217,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"